  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Subjects referred to a sleep clinic had polysomnography (PSG), clinic BP measurements,
      24-hour ABP monitoring and HBP monitoring using a device (Microlife WatchBP HomeN) that
      allows daytime (3 days, 2 duplicate readings/day) and automated nighttime BP measurement (3
      nights, 3 readings/night).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
